7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ea3ng C m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 18h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c v\u1edbi hai b\u1ea3ng A v\u00e0 B, b\u1ea3ng C c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef ASIAD 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 thay v\u00ec 4 \u0111\u1ed9i tranh t\u00e0i. V\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e1 th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang b\u1ea3ng C c\u00f9ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan. M\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m trong tay c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n x\u1ee9 hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/20180816_100127.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n n\u00f3i th\u00eam l\u00e0 3 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra, Th\u00e1i Lan ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 0-2. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n th\u1ebf, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng C sau \u0111\u00e2y 2 ng\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ec3 ganh \u0111ua v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi Th\u00e1i Lan. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, ngay c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng chi\u1ec1u nay c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ebfm v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ec7nh l\u1ec7nh ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u01b0a ra cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. \u201cG\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong c\u1ee7a \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 99%. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n l\u00e3o luy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7t Nam: H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn; Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u1ecb Ki\u1ec1u, H\u1ed3ng Nhung, Ph\u1ea1m Th\u1ecb T\u01b0\u01a1i, Th\u00f9y Dung; Tuy\u1ebft Dung, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Li\u1ec5u, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb V\u1ea1n, M\u1ef9 Anh; Hu\u1ef3nh Nh\u01b0, H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn. <br>\r\nTh\u00e1i Lan: Nattaruja; Warunee, Sunisan, Natthakarn, Kanjanaporn; Kanjana, Rattikan, Orathai, Pikul, Silawan; Taneekarn.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2540","checkdouble":"194816"},{"date":"15:12 19/08","title":"Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn MU kh\u00f3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong top 4 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-thua-nhan-mu-kho-can-dich-trong-top-4-mua-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng Man United kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch trong top 4 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00c1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Sir Alex Ferguson gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Jose Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man United s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u n\u1ebfu c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong top 4 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn MU kh\u00f3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong top 4 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn MU kh\u00f3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong top 4 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/mourinho-thua-nhan-mu-kho-can-dich-trong-top-4-mua-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho bi quan v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o top 4 Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111ang ch\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua top 4\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cLiverpool \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Chelsea c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Man City c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Tottenham c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ti\u00eau 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t Kane hay Eriksen th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. V\u00ec v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Arsenal c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pochettino-se-khong-tu-choi-neu-duoc-moi-dan-dat-mu-172-194725.html\">Pochettino s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-cu-mu-khang-dinh-sanchez-khong-phai-bom-xit-172-194719.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Sanchez kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i bom x\u1ecbt</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2539","checkdouble":"194817"},{"date":"16:56 19/08","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng D Asiad 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/10-7412-1534671506_600x0.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: 1-0<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: Quang H\u1ea3i (3')</div>\r\n<hr>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/19/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Nhat-Ban-hiep-1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/link-sopcast/link-xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-asiad-2018-302-194819.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/link-xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/link-sopcast/link-xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-asiad-2018-302-194819.html\">Link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nLink xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng link c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8, vi\u1ec7c th\u1eafng hay thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 tung ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c hay V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt chi\u1ec1u Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt 19/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/10-7412-1534671506_600x0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Quang H\u1ea3i gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">TUy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1ea3m \u0111i s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m. Ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, khi\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0m v\u1ed1n, l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eafng thua ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 tung ra kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o trong c\u00e1c pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nhanh b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ebb g\u00e3y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u00f4i qua v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u1edf m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e0nh ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1m ngh\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi l\u00e0 1-0. N\u1ebfu t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean t\u1edbi h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 \u1edf 1 trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2538","checkdouble":"194818"},{"date":"15:24 19/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/u23-thai-lan-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Uzbekistan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan vs Olympic Uzbekistan b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nU23 Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1eebng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ASIAD 2014 n\u00ean t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 th\u1ea5p \u1edf Asiad 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u00e0o ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 v\u00e0 \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn chia tay ASIAD ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u00f2a 2 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi U23 Qatar v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t U23 Bangladesh v\u1ed1n thua xa v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tay, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng m\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp b\u1edfi \u1edf c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i (U23 Qatar vs U23 Bangladesh) c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p U23 Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng Uzbekistan.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, U23 Uzbekistan - \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m Asiad 2018 - \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ea v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. H\u1ecd chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Bangladesh, ti\u1ebfp sau l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u00f2n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng h\u01a1n g\u1ea5p b\u1ed9i khi \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p U23 Qatar \u0111\u1ebfn 6-0. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady h\u1ecd s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1edf h\u1eefu lu\u00f4n ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i. Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng U23 Uzbekistan th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Uzbekistan tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Uzbekistan tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Truc-tiep-U23-Thai-Lan-vs-U23-Uzbekistan-tran-dau-Asiad-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2537","checkdouble":"194820"},{"date":"15