00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span>U23 UAE vs U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c: 1-2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nU23 UAE m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 b\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Syria v\u00e0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng U23 Timor Lester 4-1, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 U23 Syria. Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i n\u00e0y, U23 UAE ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp trong khi U23 Syria ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p U23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi tay h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, U23 UAE n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 th\u1eb3ng (d\u00e0nh cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u) th\u00ec b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p U23 Syria \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 \u0110\u00f4ng\u00a0Timor th\u00ec l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng - b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng. Th\u1ef1c ra, n\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 b\u1edfi v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tay th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m 4 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf 6 b\u1ea3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 U23 UAE c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1eb1ng 2 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ghi 9 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ph\u1ec9a v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng. U23 Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00ean h\u1ecd m\u00e0 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, U23 UAE kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang tai bang C sau 2 luot tran\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/bang-C.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2534","checkdouble":"194792"},{"date":"09:49 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor vs U23 Syria 19h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/nhan-dinh-u23-dong-timor-vs-u23-syria-19h00-ngay-198-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Old Trafford chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng ra \u0111i khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng sau ba n\u0103m, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man Utd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5p th\u1ecfm \u00e2u lo v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t \u0111i David De Gea, tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c Chelsea ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00ec Kepa Arrizabalanga. N\u00f3i chung, c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 y\u00ean v\u1ecb v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1ebf n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c De Gea ra \u0111i trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/mourinho-khang-dinh-de-gea-co-gia-0-dong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Man Utd d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c anh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tin vui \u0111\u1ebfn cho to\u00e0n Old Trafford theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1 h\u00f3m h\u1ec9nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 0 \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u00eau qu\u00fd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng suy ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00f4i khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta qu\u00ean th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Gi\u1edd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 Alisson v\u00e0 Kepa, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a David r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1edbt gi\u00e1 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho ai h\u1ebft, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 CLB, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho MU. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec ph\u1ea7n vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea3 ba b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet-172-194190.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/klopp-phan-khoi-khi-kepa-pha-ky-luc-cua-alisson.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet-172-194190.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng: B\u1ed1n th\u1eadp ni\u00ean b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f3a m\u1ed9t t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u1ecb bi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. Ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n Alisson v\u00e0 Kepa c\u0169ng l\u00e0 hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2533","checkdouble":"194793"},{"date":"10:15 19/08","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Khi m\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c hay bu\u00f4ng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i?\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>B\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh thay \u0111\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D, b\u1edfi l\u00fac n\u00e0y hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang b\u1eb1ng nhau \u1edf m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean BXH. C\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n n\u00e0o, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, n\u1ebfu hai \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00f2a nhau trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00ec theo lu\u1eadt, c\u1ea3 hai s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00fac n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p x\u1ebfp nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Malaysia, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Goc-nhin-Olympic-Viet-Nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-Nhat-Ban-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng D ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1ea5t hay nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi quan tr\u1ecdng?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, n\u1ebfu Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, theo c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n chia c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B (c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan, Qatar), ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng E (Bahrain, Kyrgyzstan, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea3ng F (Iran, Saudi Arabia hay Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c g\u1eb7p to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Malaysia v\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1eeda th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Olympic Malaysia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng khi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i trong khu v\u1ef1c \u0110N\u00c1, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o e ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Malaysia. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Ong Kim Swee t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1edd toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch tr\u00ean, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea5t gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8, m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u00edt c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u thay cho V\u0103n Thanh b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Khi \u0111\u00f3 V\u0103n Thanh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Goc-nhin-Olympic-Viet-Nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-Nhat-Ban-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd c\u00f9ng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. Song c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng hay \u0110\u1ee9c Huy. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n khi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 cho Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i. Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u00f2ng trong.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n h\u1ebft vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u r\u1ee7i ro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Khi m\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Thanh hay Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng,\u2026 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n th\u00ec s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Park Hang Seo\" title=\"Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103n HLV\u00a0Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tung \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00ecnh L\u1ee3i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n. C\u1ea3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u1eeba khao kh\u00e1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn, v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia-168-194784.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia-168-194784.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): Khi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 19/8, c\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan-168-194746.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan-168-194746.html\">HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung: \u201c\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan\u201d</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 18 di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 18h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194745.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194745.html\">B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD</span><br>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan, SiamSport m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t ASIAD 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194711.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/11/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194711.html\">Thua s\u1ed1c Malaysia, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTheo c\u00e1ch chia b\u1ea3ng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2532","checkdouble":"194794"},{"date":"11:01 19/08","title":"Sarri gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u00ec sao Chelsea b\u1ecb l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/sarri-giai-thich-vi-sao-chelsea-bi-loi-nguoc-dong-trong-hiep-mot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd qua \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Arsenal v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ba \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Marcos Alonso t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u1edf th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/sarri-giai-thich-vi-sao-chelsea-bi-loi-nguoc-dong-trong-hiep-mot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn hai b\u00e0n ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh tan th\u00e0nh m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng b\u1ed1n ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Iwobi tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Maurizio Sarri vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd sau tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf: \u201cTh\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u1edbi ba \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00fang v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00ean b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngay t\u1eeb trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u00f3.\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1ef1 ly \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o gi\u00e3n ra qu\u00e1 xa v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nhau. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 15 ph\u00fat m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u01a1i pressing \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7, ch\u00ednh th\u1ebf m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn 4-5 l\u1ea7n s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 chao \u0111\u1ea3o t\u1eeb Arsenal.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League 2018/19 sau hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u00e1u \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i. V\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Sarri s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn St. James\u2019 Park l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Newcastle.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Video tr\u1eadn Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</h2>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2531","checkdouble":"194795"}]}